snippet.title: Bridgebourn - Official Demo Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
Bridgebourn is an isometric fantasy exploration RPG adventure game developed by Bamboo's Bazaar LLC. Players will assemble a party of adventurers to discover secrets, treasures, and fight whatever lurks in their path using spells and powerful weapons. Bridgebourn is coming to PC at a later date with a demo available now.

#Bridgebourn
